# brk -- susp input file
#
# Simple suspension species swirling flow in a cylindrical geometry
#  --one material block-

 1        # element block ID
 4        # number of basic eqnvar
 0 3 1 1  # momentum equation
 4 1 1 1  # species_bulk
 9 1 1 1  # pressure
30 1 1 1  # shear rate
 
